        Notifikasi Push
      </div>
      <!-- State: loading -->
      <div id="pushLoading" style="text-align:center;padding:16px;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px">
        <div class="spinner" style="margin:0 auto 8px"></div>
        Mengecek status...
      </div>
      <!-- State: tidak support -->
      <div id="pushNotSupported" style="display:none">
        <div style="background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:12px;padding:14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-align:center">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 8px;opacity:.4"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 006 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 01-3.46 0"/></svg>
          Browser ini tidak mendukung push notification.<br>Gunakan Chrome atau aplikasi Android.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- State: permission blocked -->
      <div id="pushBlocked" style="display:none">
        <div style="background:#fef3c7;border:1px solid #fde68a;border-radius:12px;padding:14px;font-size:12px;color:#92400e">
          <b>Notifikasi diblokir.</b><br>Buka pengaturan browser → Site Settings → Notifications → Allow untuk domain ini.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- State: belum subscribe -->
      <div id="pushOff" style="display:none">
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.6">
          Aktifkan untuk mendapat notifikasi otomatis:<br>
          <b>• H-3</b> sebelum jatuh tempo &nbsp;<b>• H-1</b> pengingat akhir &nbsp;<b>• H+0</b> hari jatuh tempo &nbsp;<b>• Setelah overdue</b>
        </p>
        <button class="btn-save" id="btnEnablePush" onclick="enablePush()">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" style="display:inline;margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 006 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 01-3.46 0"/></svg>
          Aktifkan Notifikasi
        </button>
      </div>
      <!-- State: sudah subscribe -->
      <div id="pushOn" style="display:none">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:12px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:14px">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#dcfce7;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
